					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1304786&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610163625" alt="TL333s" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1304786)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;" >TL333s</a></span> <span class="odate time_1396297280 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">31 Mar 2014 20:21</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2002563">
									

<p>That was amazing. And yet, for all the excellent writing and characterization and good use of skips, the one thing I'm gonna comment on is the guy mentioning that he would have commissioned a Telekill room if it had been &quot;ten years ago&quot;. I loved that.</p>

							</div>

								
					
