					<span class="printuser deleted" data-id="1361261"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--images/avatars/default/a16.png" alt=""/>(account deleted)</span> <span class="odate time_1396466044 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 Apr 2014 19:14</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2004701">
									

<p>Outstanding. This could have very easily gone into &quot;overwrought Special Girl emo&quot; territory, but it was handled deftly and executed well. The juxtaposition between the two skips was nicely done and felt thematically coherent, the emotion in the piece is earned and therefore effective, and I liked the interaction between the Foundation personnel. This is a bit of a different Foundation than what I imagine when I'm writing, but this was done well enough and rang true enough that I enjoyed it immensely.</p>
<p>Upvoted enthusiastically.</p>

							</div>

								
					
